title: Frankfurt: 1-Hour Panorama Boat Cruise on the river Main
meeting_point: Look for the KD Ticket Office with the red, blue, and white KD logo, located on the Mainkai (close to the bridge Eisener Steg). Your boat will depart right in front of the ticket office. Proceed to board the ship and present your QR-Code ticket as you enter the ship. Getting to the landing-stage by public transport: Underground station Dom/Römer or tram stop Römer/Paulskirche, both of which are a 5-minute walk from the landing-stage. Getting to the landing-stage by car: The nearest multi-storey car park is Dom/Römer in Domstraße 1. On the car park routing system follow D = Dom. From there approx. 5 min. walk to the KD landing-stage.
